{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/button\/hidden()"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hides this view unconditionally."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"hidden","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","text":"Return Value","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A hidden view."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Hidden views are invisible and can’t receive or respond to interactions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, they do remain in the view hierarchy and affect layout. Use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this modifier if you want to include a view for layout purposes, but","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"don’t want it to display.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["HStack {","    Image(systemName: \"a.circle.fill\")","    Image(systemName: \"b.circle.fill\")","    Image(systemName: \"c.circle.fill\")","        .hidden()","    Image(systemName: \"d.circle.fill\")","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The third circle takes up space, because it’s still present, but"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"OpenSwiftUI doesn’t draw it onscreen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to conditionally include a view in the view hierarchy, use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"if"},{"type":"text","text":" statement instead:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["VStack {","    HStack {","        Image(systemName: \"a.circle.fill\")","        Image(systemName: \"b.circle.fill\")","        if !isHidden {","            Image(systemName: \"c.circle.fill\")","        }","        Image(systemName: \"d.circle.fill\")","    }","    Toggle(\"Hide\", isOn: $isHidden)","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Depending on the current value of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isHidden"},{"text":" state variable in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"example above, controlled by the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" instance, OpenSwiftUI draws","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the circle or completely omits it from the layout.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button\/hidden()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Button"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP0aB2UIE6hiddenQryF::SYNTHESIZED::s:11OpenSwiftUI6ButtonV","remoteSource":{"fileName":"HiddenModifier.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUI\/Modifier\/ViewModifier\/HiddenModifier.swift#L283"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"hidden()","modules":[{"name":"OpenSwiftUI","relatedModules":["OpenSwiftUICore"]}],"platforms":[{"beta"